      <title>FinanceBot был дописан и выложен</title>
      <link>https://zertmark.github.io/site_for_practice/blog/2025/05/15/financebot-%D0%B1%D1%8B%D0%BB-%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BF%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%B0%D0%BD-%D0%B8-%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B5%D0%BD/</link>
